Selena — The Abyssal Witch (Tiny, Elegant, Predatory Silhouette): Standing before the First Fallen, one hand resting on the trunk, is Selena. Her silhouette, though miniature, is rendered with the precision of a master miniaturist, capturing every detail of her dual, deceptive nature:

